---
title: SuperQuick Tortellini in Tomato Sausage Sauce with Parmesan Cheese
description: A delicious tomato ragu with sausage doesn't have to simmer for hours to pack a punch! This sauce, tossed with tender cheese tortellini, is packed with flavour and is on the table in 15 minutes.

